# List of desired criteria for authentication systems that the experts mentioned during the survey:
- simplicity of the authentication mechanisms
- familarity of the user with the authentication mechanisms
- number of different authentication mechanisms
- number of authnetications in a path
- availability of the authentication mechanisms
- universality of the authentication mechanisms (adapted to ecosystem)
- sensivity of the service
- implementation costs
- durability of the authetication mechanisms
- environment
- battery usage
- quality of support for the use of the authentication mechanisms
- time performance
- maintainability

